{"tid":2252624,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"★膽小勿入！外媒：iOS 14.1 災情回報總整理","createTime":"2020-10-21T14:54:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T08:04:34.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"af4c5bf2ddddb6cad4246be880e95f9c45f5e158","tid":2252624,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T14:54:55.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">iOS 14.1 災情回報總整理</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>iOS 系統</strong><br />\n<br />\n無法連線到 Apple Watch<br />\n熱點分享給電腦(macbook pro)會斷線<br />\n鍵盤有時候還是會卡頓<br />\n螢幕會變很暗 主畫面滑動有延遲<br />\n聯絡人地址地圖無法顯示<br />\n相簿中照片無法編輯<br />\n使用iTunes更新，依舊出現-4000錯誤<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>App錯誤</strong><br />\n<br />\n出現誤判閃退或卡頓情況App：Watch App、LINE、IG、MB3、原神、Google Cardboard、<br />\nLINE無法傳送照片<br />\n對方播出line我手機不會響。先打電話給我後，在播line就會響，重新開機又是一樣<br />\nLINE語音斷線，不然就是網路整個不見再恢復正常<br />\nFacebook 內建瀏覽器和手機通知狀態列快速滑動時會斷觸<br />\nYouTube全螢幕模式出現「小工具欄」<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;. 資料整理中<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mrmad.com.tw/ios14-1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmrmad.com.tw%2Fios14-1&d=z3Qy88JfdbGSADH60DObPfYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=5d436ac8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mrmad.com.tw/ios14-1</a>"},{"pid":"e6e1b5407ad9fc6e45666b18eefd792168d85976","tid":2252624,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T14:55:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"028663028c104eb7c2c36980755761eb5160a24f","tid":2252624,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T14:56:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa